109
00:06:20,171 --> 00:06:21,297
- I'm curious.
- Me too.

110
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:23,132
- I'm curious.
- It's the last test.

111
00:06:23,216 --> 00:06:24,592
- He can stand out.
- Yes.

112
00:06:24,675 --> 00:06:26,302
- It's that point.
- The last test.

113
00:06:31,057 --> 00:06:32,141
