152
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:28,484
The most heart-fluttering moment?

153
00:09:41,205 --> 00:09:42,790
- Oh, my.
- Goodness.

154
00:09:42,873 --> 00:09:44,125
She must be thirsty.

155
00:09:46,085 --> 00:09:47,253
